Sentencas: One of the most important challenges for further development of solid oxide fuel cells is to design new electrodes which operate at intermediate temperatures.
Titulo: Novel Pr0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3:Ce0.8Sm0.2O2 composite nanotubes for energy conversion and storage

Sentencas: In this sense, the formation of nanostructures of the Pr0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3:Ce0.8Sm0.2O2 composite and their characterization have been carried out.
Titulo: Novel Pr0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3:Ce0.8Sm0.2O2 composite nanotubes for energy conversion and storage

Sentencas: These nanostructures have been synthesized using polymeric membranes with 0.1 mu m pore size as templates.
Titulo: Novel Pr0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3:Ce0.8Sm0.2O2 composite nanotubes for energy conversion and storage

Sentencas: The electronic microscopy has been used in order to confirm the dimensions of the obtained nanotubes with a wall thickness of 20 nm.
Titulo: Novel Pr0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3:Ce0.8Sm0.2O2 composite nanotubes for energy conversion and storage

Sentencas: The impedance spectroscopy measurements reveal the good performance of these nanostructured materials and the effect that the nanostructures and the addition of a pure ionic conductor have on the electrochemical performance.
Titulo: Novel Pr0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3:Ce0.8Sm0.2O2 composite nanotubes for energy conversion and storage

Sentencas: The synthesized nanostructured composite exhibits an area specific resistance (ASR) value smaller than that obtained for the sample without the nanostructured morphology together with the addition of the pure ionic conductor.
Titulo: Novel Pr0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3:Ce0.8Sm0.2O2 composite nanotubes for energy conversion and storage
